  "prompt": "Do boys get friendzoned?",
  "response": "Yes, boys can be \"friendzoned,\" which means they might develop romantic feelings for someone who considers them only as a friend and does not wish to pursue a romantic relationship with them. The concept of the \"friendzone\" is not limited to any one gender; it can happen to anyone, regardless of their gender, when feelings in a relationship are not reciprocated as desired. It's important in any relationship to communicate openly and respect each other's feelings and boundaries.",
